// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0890 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: d3c9e9b9-92ac-53e6-92e9-789e604e969a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
